Ooh, yeah.
You know, Milt, I brought
the family album along.

1209
01:23:43,885 --> 01:23:46,615
<i>It's back at the hotel.
Maybe I should pop back...
Ah!</i>

1210
01:23:46,688 --> 01:23:49,088
You don't have to
go now, do you?
Nonsense. Nonsense.

