l... I am a lucky guy.

1230
01:24:48,216 --> 01:24:50,548
<i>Annie's one in a million.</i>

1231
01:24:50,618 --> 01:24:54,452
You jerk. I am gonna
come out there and
kick the shit out of you.

1232
01:24:54,522 --> 01:24:57,423
