1235
01:25:01,729 --> 01:25:04,562
Can you believe it?
The car didn't meet him
at the airport.

1236
01:25:04,632 --> 01:25:07,999
<i>Listen, can you stay put
for 45 minutes,
and I'll be right there?</i>

1237
01:25:08,069 --> 01:25:11,630
Good idea, Jonathan.
Oh, yes.
What a sweet thing to do.

1238
01:25:11,706 --> 01:25:13,970
Okay. All right.
I'll see you.

1239
01:25:24,085 --> 01:25:26,076
Give me that.
Wait. Wait.

1240
01:25:26,154 --> 01:25:29,920
I think you've had enough.
Don't spill it!
Don't...

