Rammed this baby right through
city council. That's the kind
of building commissioner he is.

1247
01:26:11,366 --> 01:26:14,335
I'm sure we can do
more business together
in the future.

1248
01:26:14,402 --> 01:26:16,393
I think we might be
laying the foundation...

1249
01:26:16,471 --> 01:26:20,703
