1261
01:26:53,374 --> 01:26:56,275
The medical center's due
to start construction here
next week.

1262
01:26:56,344 --> 01:26:59,074
I need the site cleared
before the weekend is over.

1263
01:26:59,147 --> 01:27:01,081
